                  Rehabilitación Oral
                </a>
              </li>
              <li>
                <a href="/servicios" class="flex items-center gap-2 hover:text-white transition-all duration-300 group">
                  <span class="w-1 h-1 bg-cyan-300 rounded-full group-hover:bg-white transition-colors"></span>
                  Implantes Dentales
                </a>
              </li>
              <li>
                <a href="/servicios" class="flex items-center gap-2 hover:text-white transition-all duration-300 group">
                  <span class="w-1 h-1 bg-cyan-300 rounded-full group-hover:bg-white transition-colors"></span>
